{
  "id": "adv_bond_rui_01_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……おはようございます、莉央さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yawn… Good morning‚ Rio-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7000000358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、瑠依。……おはようって、もう十時だけど\nこの時間に起きるなんて、めずらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Rui. …good morning? It's already 10 o'clock\nIt's unusual for you to wake up this late",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1000000041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "雫から借りたアイドルのDVDを観てて……\n夜更かししちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm watching an idol DVD that Shizuku lent me…\nI stayed up late",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666666707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "他のアイドルのステージ演出を参考にしたくて\nメモを取りながら観てたら、いつの間にか外が明るくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to refer to other idols stage performances‚\nso I was watching it while taking notes‚ and before I knew it‚ it was bright outside",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2000000041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依は本当に真面目ね\nまるで{user}さんみたいだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui is really diligent\nYou're just like {user}-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.0000000041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことないです！\n私が{user}さんと同じだなんて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ that's not true!\nI'm not like {user}-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5333333374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。真面目なところが似てるのよ\nところで、朝ご飯は食べる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. That kind of diligent side is similar\nBy the way‚ will you have breakfast?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.4333346089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……何か適当に食べようと思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I was thinking of just grabbing something",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7333346089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ありもので良ければ作ってあげるけど\nこの材料なら……そうね。パンケーキでいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can make something with what we have if you'd like\nWith these ingredients… Okay. How about pancake?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.4666679423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "いいんですか？　ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1000012756,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cup-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.998788000001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、どうぞ\nそこまで凝ったものではないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No problem. Here you go\nIt's not that special though",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.1000012756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "バナナやイチゴが乗ってて、美味しそうですね！\nあ、このままでも美味しいと思うんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With bananas and strawberries on top‚ it looks good!\nAh‚ I think it's already good as it is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.9333346089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "もっと美味しくなるよう、トッピング追加しますね\nえーっと、確かお菓子の棚に……あった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll add some toppings to make it even better\nLet's seeー I think I saw some in the snack cupboard… here it is",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3000012756,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 15699.59792680001
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_plasticbag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13253.163595800004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、ジャムとかも必要だった？　なら……え？\nちょ、ちょっと！　パンケーキに何かけてるのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah‚ did you need jam or something? Then… eh?\nW-Wait! What are you putting on the pancake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.2333320658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "マカロニグラタン味のグミです\n美味しく食べたいので、一袋全部かけちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a macaroni gratin flavored gummy\nI wanted to make it taste even better‚ so I put the whole bag on",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9666653991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "マカロニグラタン味のグミです……じゃないわよ！\nそんな真顔でパンケーキの上にぶちまけるなんて……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Macaroni gratin flavored gummy… that's not!\nSprinkling it on pancake with such a serious face…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2333320658,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "というか、何その味！　聞いたことないんだけど\nそれにかけすぎよ！　パンケーキが見えないじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Above all‚ what does that taste like! I've never heard of it\nAnd you put too much! I can't even see the pancakes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5333381693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "塩味を追加した方が、甘みが増して美味しいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought adding a salty flavor would bring out the sweetness more",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8666745544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ！？　塩味って……もっとチョイスあったでしょ\nそもそもカロリーの摂り過ぎ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa!? Salty flavor… there were so many other options\nFirst of all‚ you are consuming too many calories!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3333412211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。この後走るので。それより……\n莉央さんも食べてみますか？　美味しいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. I'm going for a run later. By the way…\nWould you like to try it too‚ Rio-san? It's good",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.1666745544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……遠慮しとくわ\n見てるだけで胸焼けしそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'll pass\nJust looking at it gives me heartburn…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333412211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "それでは改めて、いただきます……もぐもぐ……ん～！\n莉央さんのパンケーキ、凄く美味しいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ once agan‚ let's eat… munch munch… yum~!\nRio-san's pancake is so delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0666745544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_rui_01_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ありがとう\nはぁ。瑠依が美味しいって喜んでるならそれでいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… thank you\nHaa. Rui said it's delicious‚ so that's fine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.2666745544,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}